Relies on the pandas package


Usage:

    python nbayes.py training_set test_set output_file

  OR

compile using Cython:

$ cython --embed nbayes.py
$ gcc -Ofast -I /usr/include/python2.7 nbayes.c -o nbayesexe -lpython2.7 -lm -lutil -ldl

then run:

$ ./nbayesexe training_set test_set output_file

